isaacvetter commented on Issue #169

Hi Kenn,

This page is outside of the normative-track content and is intended to be supplemental material that is not part of the specification and is not being balloted.

Thank you for pointing out this broken link. We'll update the top level index page to fix it's link to the Event Catalog.

Isaac

isaacvetter commented on Issue #169:

Due to the refactoring of the event catalog, we no longer has a single url that could be the target of an Event Catalog link; however, the event catalog is much more visible on the site due to its being on the menu.

I'm removing the broken link to fix this issue. This issue is also a duplicate of #138.
